title: Introducing etnies Womens Fall 13 Collection
description:
etnies just introduced the fall 13 women’s collection with a video look book. The brand’s new footwear line offers everything from boots to flats for autumn. The girls in the look book stroll through city and enjoy some downtime in the combat boot styled etnies Regiment, and Senix D Mid Tops, Caprice and Venus flats. Several of the styles in the collection are part of the Buy a Shoe, Plant a Tree reforestation program, and the fall collection is now available globally.
View Collection: etnies.com/shop/womens/fall-13
